reviews: This table is Elegant as described, it is truly Beautiful. It arrived with a few dings which made me sad but I could not send it back so I will live with them.
Beautiful table. Looks perfect in my kitchen. Craftsmanship is great. The price is excellent for this table. I have gotten so many compliments on it.
All the item has got four star great products
Substance is this table. Beautiful wood and can seat 6-8 if using smaller chairs. Beautiful!!
I love the style and look of this table it is heavy duty and well made it seems it will last a very long time. I recommend it as a formal dining table its that nice. 👍🏼
